   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Of the granary of the horiodeiktia of Karanis, of the dekaprotoi Severinus and Andrias, of the crop of year 14 and 13 and 6, in the name of Sarapammon, the brother of Chairemon, through beasts of the same, one donkey, equal 1. Year 15 and 14 and 7, Mecheir 28.</ab>
